ZH: 双手合十，祈求平安。
EN: Joining both hands together to pray for peace.

ZH: 双手握紧，充满力量。
EN: Clasping both hands tightly, filled with strength.

ZH: 双手握住我的手，陪伴我走下去。
EN: Holding my hand with both hands, accompanying me along the way.

ZH: 双手捂住嘴巴，不让自己说出来。
EN: Covering the mouth with both hands, preventing oneself from speaking out.

ZH: 双手托起这片蓝天，为我们遮蔽风雨。
EN: Holding up this piece of blue sky with both hands, shielding us from the storm.

ZH: 双手合抱，抓住机会。
EN: Embracing with both hands, seize the opportunity.

ZH: 双手拥抱，表达深深的爱意。
EN: Embracing with both hands, expressing deep love.

ZH: 双手伸出来，表示友好。
EN: Extending both hands, showing friendliness.

ZH: 双手抚摸着小猫，温柔而细致。
EN: Caressing the kitten with both hands, gentle and delicate.

ZH: 双手摸着冰凉的瓷杯，感受到清凉。
EN: Touching the cold porcelain cup with both hands, feeling the coolness.

ZH: 双手翻开了那本神秘的书，探索其中的秘密。
EN: Opening the mysterious book with both hands, exploring its secrets.

ZH: 双手交叉，安静思考。
EN: Crossing both hands, thinking quietly.

ZH: 双手拍打水面，溅起一朵朵水花。
EN: Clapping the water surface with both hands, splashing water droplets.

